1\";s:5:\"feeds\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"pages\";s:1:\"1\";}s:9:\"query_var\";s:13:\"post_type_key\";s:14:\"query_var_name\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"can_export\";b:1;s:16:\"delete_with_user\";b:0;s:20:\"register_meta_box_cb\";s:0:\"\";}','Treatments','treatments','publish','closed','closed','','post_type_64e551d323abe','','','2023-08-23 00:25:30','2023-08-23 00:25:30','',0,'http://dgrace-medspa.test/?post_type=acf-post-type&#038;p=111',0,'acf-post-type','',0),(113,1,'2023-08-23 00:28:53','2023-08-23 00:28:53','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>IPL (Intense Pulse Light) Photofacial is a popular, minimal downtime treatment for the correction of pigment changes and redness associated with facial flushing and rosacea. IPL works by using light energy from a combination of wavelengths to penetrate the dermis while leaving the epidermis (outside layer of skin) untouched. There is no damage to the skin’s surface, and patients have only minimal redness and slight swelling immediately after the procedure. IPL treatments can be performed on the face, chest, arms, and hands. Usually, 2 to 4 treatments are recommended to achieve maximum effectiveness (depending on your skin type and color).<br>The benefits of IPL skin rejuvenation include:<br>● Reduction of hyperpigmentation and reversal of the signs of sun damage<br>● Improvement of redness associated with rosacea.<br>● Removal of unwanted facial veins<br>● Improvement to skin texture and pore size<br>● Increase collagen production.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','IPL PHOTO REJUVENATION','','publish','closed','closed','','ipl-photo-rejuvenation','','','2023-08-23 00:28:53','2023-08-23 00:28:53','',0,'http://dgrace-medspa.test/?post_type=dgrace_treatment&#038;p=113',0,'dgrace_treatment','',0),(114,1,'2023-08-23 00:28:17','2023-08-23 00:28:17','','IPL_PHOTO_REJUVENATION','','inherit','open','closed','','ipl_photo_rejuvenation','','','2023-08-23 00:28:17','2023-08-23 00:28:17','',113,'http://dgrace-medspa.test/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/IPL_PHOTO_REJUVENATION-.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(115,1,'2023-08-23 00:31:15','2023-08-23 00:31:15','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Laser is the best solution for unwanted hair and to avoid the inflammation from it, which leads to folliculitis and skin darkening.<br>Laser hair removal is your solution. You can enjoy not having to shave for a long time, as it is a method of hair reduction, causing the hair follicle to weaken or stop producing hair. At CaliMed Wellness &amp; Spa, you can find certified technicians experienced in laser hair removal/reduction.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Laser hair removal has become the new popular alternative to traditional shaving. It is considered to be an aesthetic procedure where the hair is removed in approximately 8 to 14 sessions, depending on the area of the body. Laser hair removal is a process in which hair follicles are treated with laser light, resulting in permanent hair reduction or removal. Laser hair removal is safe, effective, and provides long-lasting results. With the introduction of advanced laser technology, waxing, razor bumps and painful electrolysis are finally becoming a thing of the past. After the laser hair removal treatment, you can expect to be hair free for several months without downtime. The hair will eventually regrow, but there will be considerably less growth and the hair appears to be much thinner.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The most common treated areas for women include legs, bikini, underarms, upper lip and stomach and the most common treated areas for men are facial hair, ears, shoulders, back and chest.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Services offered for Women:<br>● Face<br>● Eyebrows<br>● Upper Lip<br>● Chin<br>● Chest<br>● Under Arms<br>● Arms &amp; Hands<br>● Abdomen<br>● Legs &amp; Feet<br>● Bikini &amp; Brazilian</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Services offered for Men:<br>● Face<br>● Beard<br>● Neck &amp; Chest<br>● Back &amp; Shoulders<br>● Arms &amp; Hands<br>● Under Arms<br>● Abdomen<br>● Legs &amp; Feet</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','LASER HAIR REMOVAL','','publish','closed','closed','','laser-hair-removal','','','2023-08-23 00:31:15','2023-08-23 00:31:15','',0,'http://dgrace-medspa.test/?post_type=dgrace_treatment&#038;p=115',0,'dgrace_treatment','',0),(116,1,'2023-08-23 00:32:14','2023-08-23 00:32:14','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Also known as \"liposuction without surgery\", is a non-invasive treatment to shape the body and eliminate fat, achieving satisfactory results in volume reduction from the first session. It is recommended a minimum of 3 to 12 consecutive sessions for better results.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This treatment does not treat flaccidity; it\'s only designed to target adipose cells and it also helps to minimize the appearance of cellulite.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cavitation consists of applying low frequency ultrasound, generating micro bubbles in the fat cells without damaging surrounding tissues. The system is very selective, ensuring that the target is the subcutaneous fat.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','ULTRASOUND CAVITATION','','publish','closed','closed','','ultrasound-cavitation','','','2023-08-23 00:32:14','2023-08-23 00:32:14','',0,'http://dgrace-medspa.test/?post_type=dgrace_treatment&#038;p=116',0,'dgrace_treatment','',0),(117,1,'2023-08-23 00:32:07','2023-08-23 00:32:07','','ultrasound-fat-cavitation','','inherit','open','closed','','ultrasound-fat-cavitation','','','2023-08-23 00:32:07','2023-08-23 00:32:07','',116,'http://dgrace-medspa.test/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ultrasound-fat-cavitation.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(118,1,'2023-08-23 00:33:59','2023-08-23 00:33:59','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Improve clarity and even skin tone to reveal a radiant, glowing, youthful complexion. This facial incorporates medical-grade alpha beta hydroxy acids 