ily Nurse Practitioner to offer more services to our prestigious clientele.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:300\">María Teresa Ormaza MSN, APRN, AGANP-BC,BSN,RN, is a Board Certified Advanced Gerontology Acute Nurse Practitioner with 11 years of experience in Critical Care and Emergency Medicine. She graduated from Nova Southeastern University with a Bachelor\'s in Nursing in 2012 and in 2022 earned her Master\'s degree in acute care nurse practice with highest honors. She currently work in a heart transplant unit and open-heart surgeries.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":98,\"width\":236,\"height\":154,\"sizeSlug\":\"medium\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-medium is-resized\"><img src=\"http://dgrace-medspa.test/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/esponja-300x196.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-98\" style=\"width:236px;height:154px\" width=\"236\" height=\"154\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"0\",\"padding\":{\"top\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide\" style=\"padding-top:0\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":56,\"width\":50,\"height\":51,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://dgrace-medspa.test/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/logo_titulos.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-56\" style=\"width:50px;height:51px