n, managing her own MedSpa in Barranquilla, Colombia for 8 years. After moving to the United States in 2014, she attended the Florida Medical College where she obtained licenses of Laser Technician, Certified Medical Electrologist, and Facial Specialist.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:300\">Juan C. Perez, FMD, RN, CCRP, obtained his credentials as Medic and Surgeon from the prestigious University of Antioquia (Colombia) in 1993 and practiced as ED and Outpatient physician and Surgeon at several renowned centers in Medellin, Colombia before moving to the United States in 1999. Graduated from the esteemed Florida International University as Registered Nurse in 2005, he has been dedicated to clinical and pharmaceutical research and also working as a Registered Nurse for our Spa. He is currently enrolled and soon to be graduated as&nbsp;a Master of Family Nurse Practitioner to offer more services to our prestigious clientele.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:300\">María Teresa Ormaza MSN, APRN, AGANP-BC,BSN,RN, is a Board Certified Advanced Gerontology Acute Nurse Practitioner with 11 years of experience in Critical Care and Emergency Medicine. She graduated from Nova Southeastern University with a Bachelor\'s in Nursing in 2012 and in 2022 earned her Master\'s degree in acute care nurse practice with highest honors. She currently work in a heart transplant unit and open-heart surgeries.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style